How PCF Works

    Three Main Parts of PCF
    ---------------------

        BOSH - Creates and Deploys VMs on top of Physical Computing Infrastructure, deploys and runs PCF. BOSH requires a
        manifest.

        Cloud Controller - Runs the apps and processes on the cloud's VMs. Balances and manages app's life-cycles.

        Gorouter - Responsible for routing traffic to the running VMs,

